{"tid":2233748,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《Resident Evil》電影重製 女主角換人","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T13:54:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8693dc372e3eb8497c7869c395d3acd967794d00","tid":2233748,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"於美國影視界幾乎一片沉寂之時，有某一個知名系列卻出乎意料地動作多多&mdash;&mdash;講緊嘅就係《Resident Evil》系列。過去一段時間，《Resident Evil》已經先後公佈Netflix真人劇集、動畫兩個計劃，而近日更加公佈第三個，就係真人版電影都會重新啟動！<br />\n<br />\n據《Deadline》報導，原版《Resident Evil》 (即係Mila Jovovich主演嗰個系列) 嘅製作公司Constantin Film將會與導演兼編劇Johannes Roberts合作，推出以「1998年浣熊市」為背景嘅「官方起源故事」電影。會由《Maze Runner》女星、今年28歲嘅Kaya Scodelario飾演Claire、Hanna John-Kamen飾演Jill、Robbie Amell飾演Chris、Avan Jogia飾演Leon，而Wesker一角就搵黎《The Umbrella Academy》嘅「一號」Tom Hopper飾演。<br />\n<br />\nJohannes Roberts指，套戲會以Capcom原作遊戲嘅頭兩集為藍本，佢希望可以重新呈現當年佢打機時感受到嘅恐怖感，同時講述一個令現在觀眾都有貼身感受嘅死城故事。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Constantin Film"},{"pid":"e84e465fed994ffbd6e6f99b19bf7546d4b014a1","tid":2233748,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/10/7/2c81bc37fa94215be9092a628ac7b61a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F10%2F7%2F2c81bc37fa94215be9092a628ac7b61a.jpg&h=e47a0fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左；Kaya Scodelario 右：Hanna John-Kamen"},{"pid":"800be6a7667265aba41b9d0b00e14894341126a6","tid":2233748,"uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"浣熊市 撚有Chris 咩<br />\n重拍得"},{"pid":"2bc208613df04403e8a65dd935fe61e5d4dd567d","tid":2233748,"uid":78892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"Jill咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47de7dee361e505b72e628a7a25d55b0608f4186","tid":2233748,"uid":121951,"like":2,"disli